Package com.versant.connector.common

Interface Summary
ConfigManager ConfigManager interface is primarily defined for integrating with non-reference application servers.
JCAConstants JCAConstants provides a list of constants used in JVI JCA Connector.
LogConstants LogConstants interface specifies constants for diff. types of log level.
Util  
 

Class Summary
DefaultConfigManager DefaultConfigManager class provides a default implementation for ConfigManager interface which is independent of any application server.
ErrorConstants ErrorConstants enumerates all the JVI JCA Connector error constants.
JCALog A static class used for logging messages.
LocalTransactionImpl LocalTransactionImpl class provides support for transactions that are managed internal to an EIS resource manager, and do not require an external transaction manager.
